defaultCompanies.description:
The Arcadia Family of Companies is a local non-profit organization committed to providing senior living excellence in a gracious, compassionate, and dynamic environment which meets the spiritual, physical, and social needs of every resident, client, and member we serve.

Our employees are the foundation for the services we provide to our residents, clients, and members. Our organization offers an environment where teamwork, mentoring, self-development, and communication are encouraged.
The Armstrong Companies are involved in all aspects of real estate, including development, design, sales, construction, property management and community philanthropy.

Gilford Sato & Associates CPA, Inc. has been providing clients personalized tax and accounting services through out Hawaii since 1994. With representative offices in Tokyo and Osaka, our certified and experience team members are equipped to handle all of your accounting needs, no matter how complex. Whether you require assistance at the corporate or personal level, we are ready to serve as your tax planners and accounting advisors. We stay up-to-date on all the regulatory and legislative developments so you don’t waste time and energy trying to make sense of all the accounting complexities.

We are an employee-owned firm based in Maui, Hawaii that specializes in civil engineering, land surveying, permitting and project management. Established in 1988, we have provided over 30 years of service to private-sector and public-sector clients in Maui County (Maui, Molokai and Lanai).

Since our humble beginnings over a century ago, Servco has remained committed to our founder’s principles of hard work, customer satisfaction, dedication to quality and service to others. Today, we recognize that these values are more important than ever, and we strive to remain true to them as our business continues to thrive and grow.
